{
  "id": "adv_event_2210_01_04",
  "title": "交差した\n運命",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "空の色が変わってゆく\n憂いも喜びも解けた色で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The color of the sky changes\nto a color that combines sadness and joy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 12.1629703522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "大人になり、どれだけ経とうとも\n素顔のままいられるよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that I can remain the same even\nas time passes as I become an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2333333333,
      "endTime": 22.775623258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "運命ここで交差して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fates crossed here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2,
      "endTime": 29.5642401695,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6666667000009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "endTime": 30.900000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、勝手に合わせちゃいました\nあんまり素敵な歌声だったので、つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I added chords to the song on my own.\nIt's such a wonderful voice that I didn't even realize it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "endTime": 39.2525844852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "お世辞はいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't give lip service",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6666666667,
      "endTime": 41.6263265292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私がそんなことを言う性格だと\n思っていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you think I was the type of person\nto say things like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8333333333,
      "endTime": 45.145684917699995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "…………思わないわね\n貴方もお姉さん同様、そういうの嫌いでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… Not really\nDon’t you hate that kind of thing too‚ like your sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666666667,
      "endTime": 51.200419348500006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、嘘は嫌いです\nでも、莉央さんは私に一つ嘘をつきましたね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I hate lies.\nBut‚ Rio-san‚ you lied to me about one thing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "endTime": 59.0333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの歌、うろ覚えだって言ってましたけど\n凄くうまいじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister's song… you said the lyrics were confusing\nYou sing really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "endTime": 65.4175051489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "バレちゃったわね。ごめんなさい\n実はこの曲、好きなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You heard it‚ Sorry\nActually‚ I like this song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "endTime": 72.1878453692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "特に、今の所の歌詞\n私達の境遇に重ねてたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In particular‚ the lyrics in the previous part\noverlap with our situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "endTime": 78.3537354906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "運命交差して、って所ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this the part where “fates crossed here”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "endTime": 82.1580271721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私と長瀬麻奈は一瞬だけ、すれ違って\nそして、もう二度と会えなくなった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me and Nagase Mana passed by for a moment\nand we will never meet again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "endTime": 90.6213724371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "その後、私は一年間、歌から離れた\nいえ、正確には離れようとしてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ I stayed away from singing for a year.\nNo‚ to be exact‚ I tried to leave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4,
      "endTime": 99.526155897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央さんは辞めなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rio-san didn't quit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "endTime": 102.4973468781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "この歌の続き、明日を強く生きる、って言葉を\n何度も口ずさむうちに、心が前を向きだしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After this song‚ as I sang the words “Live powerfully tomorrow”\nover and over again‚ my heart began to move forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "endTime": 111.54237221359999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そして、私は再びこの世界に戻る決心をした\n琴乃、私はね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I decided to go back to this world\nKotono‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8666666667,
      "endTime": 120.5511971153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "――はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――yes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666666667,
      "endTime": 121.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "この歌を通じて、長瀬麻奈にきっと何度も\n励まされたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was definitely encouraged by Mana Nagase many times\nthrough this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3666666667,
      "endTime": 128.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "私が今も歌っていられるのは、間違いなく\n彼女と、この歌に出会ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I can still sing is because\nI met her and this song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333333333,
      "endTime": 136.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "一言でいい、ありがとうって伝えたい……\n今の私を見てもらいたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even just one word… I want to say 'thank you'…\nI want her to see me as I am now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137,
      "endTime": 144.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7,
      "endTime": 146.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、ちゃんと琴乃と話してるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is Rio… talking to Kotono properly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4666666667,
      "endTime": 151.82532884280002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "遠くて暗くてよく見えませんけど\n二人とも仲良く話してるような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's hard to see because it's far away and dark‚\nbut it looks like they're both talking happily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0333333333,
      "endTime": 160.1431957114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、でも、莉央さん\n肩がちょっと震えてるかもです！\n泣いてるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but Rio-san’s\nshoulders seem to be shaking a little!\nIs she crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3333333333,
      "endTime": 165.8861764431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あの莉央さんが泣くなんてありえないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way Rio-san would cry~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0666666667,
      "endTime": 168.6166666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "馬鹿だな、莉央だって泣くことくらいあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fool‚ Rio sometimes cries too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8333333333,
      "endTime": 172.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "きっと長瀬麻奈のことを思い出してる\n莉央はいつも泣きたい時は一人で静かに泣くんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure she's thinking of Mana Nagase.\nRio always cries quietly alone when she wants to cry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.3666666667,
      "endTime": 179.8838142947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "それを知ってるってことは、葵さん\nいつも莉央さんを見守って……",
      "translations": {
